nodes.title: Rescale CFG  &  Set Last Layer
widgets_values:
-------------------- Rescale CFG ------------------
( def: 0.7 ) * (<) less adherence, softer, smoother
             * (>) more adherence, crisper detail
------------------- Set Last Layer ----------------
( def: −1 )  * tighter adherence, sharper detail
             * artifacts-semantic drift may appear

nodes.title: CFG  &  PAG
widgets_values:
------------------------- CFG ----------------------
* (<) less adherence, smoother look, more drift
* (>) more adherence, punchier detail, artifact risk
------------------------- PAG ----------------------
( 0 off ) * increasing PAG boosts diversity
( def 3 ) * but reduces stability & prompt adherence

nodes.title: Detail Daemon
widgets_values:
-- Details -------- ( def 0.0 ) ---------------------
        * negative values reduce detail
-- Bias--------- ( def: 0.0 - 0.5 ) -----------------
        * shifts peak toward earlier or later steps
--Exponent------ ( def: 0.5 – 1.0 ) -----------------
        * sigma curvature 0 = linear 1 = smooth curve

nodes.title: LoRA's Hooks
widgets_values:
- Hooks timeline: start with original Model strength, then Strength 1, then 2.
- Flow: base weights first; at 'Str 1 start' apply S1; at 'Str 2 start' apply S2.
- Strength 1 and Strength 2 are PERCENTAGES of the current Model strength.
- Example: Model=1.20, S1=80% → effective=0.96; S2=120% → effective=1.44.
* To disable hooks via timing: set 'Strength 1/2 start at %' to 100 for both.
* To disable via levels: set 'Strength 1' and 'Strength 2' sliders to 100%.
